  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "chapterTitle": "第一节 形式逻辑的对象和性质",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300135184_9_487-565",
          "range": "487-565",
          "rangeStart": 487,
          "rangeEnd": 565,
          "markText": "形式逻辑有传统与现代（即数理逻辑）之分。我们这里所说的形式逻辑主要指前者，即指一门以系统介绍传统逻辑的基本知识为主的逻辑科学，也就是现在人们常说的普通逻辑。",
          "colorStyle": 2,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1740483497,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-02-25 19:38:17",
          "chapterUid": 9,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300135184&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=487&rangeEnd=565",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/38e32ec0813ab9b4eg014437?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=487&rangeEnd=565"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300135184_36_4663-4720",
      "chapterUid": 36,
      "range": "4663-4720",
      "markText": "求同求异并用法是这样一种方法，考察两组事例，一组是由被研究现象出现的若干场合组成的，称之为正事例组；",
      "totalCount": 1238,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300135184&chapterUid=36&rangeStart=4663&rangeEnd=4720",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/38e32ec0813ab9b4eg014437?chapterUid=36&rangeStart=4663&rangeEnd=4720"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300135184_24_821-877",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "821-877",
      "markText": "如前两例中，“一个物体是固体”、“一个物体是液体”、“一个物体是气体”这三个命题就是前一个选言命题的三个选言肢；",
      "totalCount": 1236,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300135184&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=821&rangeEnd=877",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/38e32ec0813ab9b4eg014437?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=821&rangeEnd=877"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300135184_40_806-856",
      "chapterUid": 40,
      "range": "806-856",
      "markText": "任一判断或命题都有其确定的判断或命题内容，是这个判断或命题就是这个判断或命题，而不是别的判断或命题。",
      "totalCount": 1233,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300135184&chapterUid=40&rangeStart=806&rangeEnd=856",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/38e32ec0813ab9b4eg014437?chapterUid=40&rangeStart=806&rangeEnd=856"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300135184_42_1796-1836",
      "chapterUid": 42,
      "range": "1796-1836",
      "markText": "因为在一定的论域内，真理总是属于两个互相矛盾的思想中的一个，而不可能属于第三者。",
      "totalCount": 1223,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300135184&chapterUid=42&rangeStart=1796&rangeEnd=1836",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/38e32ec0813ab9b4eg014437?chapterUid=42&rangeStart=1796&rangeEnd=1836"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300135184_12_1777-1832",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "1777-1832",
      "markText": "因此我们说，“商品”概念的内涵要比“劳动产品”概念的内涵多，而“劳动产品”概念的内涵要比“商品”概念的内涵少。",
      "totalCount": 1219,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300135184&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=1777&rangeEnd=1832",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/38e32ec0813ab9b4eg014437?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=1777&rangeEnd=1832"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300135184_20_477-498",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "477-498",
      "markText": "比如：①迷信不是科学，所以，科学不是迷信；",
      "totalCount": 1205,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300135184&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=477&rangeEnd=498",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/38e32ec0813ab9b4eg014437?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=477&rangeEnd=498"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300135184_16_4938-4980",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "4938-4980",
      "markText": "若定义项直接或间接包括被定义项，则定义项本身就不明确，因而被定义项也就无法得到明确。",
      "totalCount": 1188,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300135184&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=4938&rangeEnd=4980",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/38e32ec0813ab9b4eg014437?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=4938&rangeEnd=4980"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300135184_16_5608-5669",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "5608-5669",
      "markText": "给概念下定义就是为了要明确揭示概念的内涵，因此，必须正面揭示它是什么，它具有什么性质，因而作为定义的命题必须是肯定的命题。",
      "totalCount": 1184,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300135184&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=5608&rangeEnd=5669",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/38e32ec0813ab9b4eg014437?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=5608&rangeEnd=5669"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300135184_36_6268-6339",
      "chapterUid": 36,
      "range": "6268-6339",
      "markText": "共变法是指：在其他条件不变的情况下，如果一个现象发生变化，另一个现象就随之发生变化，那么，前一现象就是后一现象的原因或部分原因。",
      "totalCount": 1182,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300135184&chapterUid=36&rangeStart=6268&rangeEnd=6339",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/38e32ec0813ab9b4eg014437?chapterUid=36&rangeStart=6268&rangeEnd=6339"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300135184_45_3464-3611",
      "chapterUid": 45,
      "range": "3464-3611",
      "markText": "必须指出的是，由于归纳论证所使用的推理形式（即论证中的论证方式）是归纳推理（推广一点说，也可包括类比推理），而归纳推理一般说来是一种或然性推理，因此，在严格的论证中，用不完全归纳推理建构的论证一般只能起辅助作用，而不宜独立地加以使用，即应当尽可能同演绎论证相结合，以保证其论证的可靠性与说服力。",
      "totalCount": 1176,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300135184&chapterUid=45&rangeStart=3464&rangeEnd=3611",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/38e32ec0813ab9b4eg014437?chapterUid=45&rangeStart=3464&rangeEnd=3611"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300135184_48_5570-5611",
      "chapterUid": 48,
      "range": "5570-5611",
      "markText": "这是指在作出归纳概括的过程中抽象不合理，如抽样片面、样本不具代表性等而产生的谬误。",
      "totalCount": 1161,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300135184&chapterUid=48&rangeStart=5570&rangeEnd=5611",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/38e32ec0813ab9b4eg014437?chapterUid=48&rangeStart=5570&rangeEnd=5611"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300135184_11_3029-3078",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "3029-3078",
      "markText": "有时，即使某人对某概念是明确的，但是，由于运用语词不当，表达出来的思想仍然不明确，别人也无法理解。",
      "totalCount": 1147,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300135184&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=3029&rangeEnd=3078",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/38e32ec0813ab9b4eg014437?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=3029&rangeEnd=3078"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300135184_43_3706-3764",
      "chapterUid": 43,
      "range": "3706-3764",
      "markText": "比如前面对“华东师范大学是一所培养人民教师的学校”这一论题的论证过程中，我们就是采用了一个直言三段论作为论证方式的。",
      "totalCount": 1145,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300135184&chapterUid=43&rangeStart=3706&rangeEnd=3764",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/38e32ec0813ab9b4eg014437?chapterUid=43&rangeStart=3706&rangeEnd=3764"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300135184_28_702-756",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "702-756",
      "markText": "两个复合命题是等值的，当且仅当在任何相同的情况下（包含相同的肢命题并且这些肢命题同真同假），它们都同真同假。",
      "totalCount": 1120,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300135184&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=702&rangeEnd=756",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/38e32ec0813ab9b4eg014437?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=702&rangeEnd=756"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300135184_20_1082-1121",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "1082-1121",
      "markText": "例如把“所有新生事物都是有生命力的”改变成“所有新生事物都不是没有生命力的”。",
      "totalCount": 1118,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300135184&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=1082&rangeEnd=1121",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/38e32ec0813ab9b4eg014437?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=1082&rangeEnd=1121"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300135184_41_705-750",
      "chapterUid": 41,
      "range": "705-750",
      "markText": "因此，“并非（A而且非A）”是说：A和非A这两个命题不能同真，亦即其中必有一个命题是假的。",
      "totalCount": 1078,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300135184&chapterUid=41&rangeStart=705&rangeEnd=750",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/38e32ec0813ab9b4eg014437?chapterUid=41&rangeStart=705&rangeEnd=750"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300135184_34_2921-2960",
      "chapterUid": 34,
      "range": "2921-2960",
      "markText": "其次，要就对象的实质方面进行比较，不要因某种表面上的相同，而忽略实质上的差异；",
      "totalCount": 1070,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300135184&chapterUid=34&rangeStart=2921&rangeEnd=2960",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/38e32ec0813ab9b4eg014437?chapterUid=34&rangeStart=2921&rangeEnd=2960"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300135184_48_4144-4201",
      "chapterUid": 48,
      "range": "4144-4201",
      "markText": "这是指在论证中对论题不作具体的论证，而仅靠不加分析地摘引权威人士的言论，以之作为论证论题正确的充分论据的一种谬误。",
      "totalCount": 1070,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300135184&chapterUid=48&rangeStart=4144&rangeEnd=4201",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/38e32ec0813ab9b4eg014437?chapterUid=48&rangeStart=4144&rangeEnd=4201"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300135184_11_2948-3007",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "2948-3007",
      "markText": "因为，概念反映客观事物的特性和本质，如果不认识事物，不了解事物的特性和本质，当然也就谈不上形成有关该事物的明确概念了。",
      "totalCount": 1054,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300135184&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=2948&rangeEnd=3007",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/38e32ec0813ab9b4eg014437?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=2948&rangeEnd=3007"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300135184_35_4714-4747",
      "chapterUid": 35,
